title: I’m An Uncouth Lady, But I Helped The Villainous Young Lord But He Ended Up Liking Me - Novel Updates
tags: Abusive Characters   Broken Engagement   European Ambience   Fallen Nobility   Female Protagonist   Hated Protagonist   Kind Love Interests   Marriage   Multiple POV   Nobles   R-15   Royalty
author: Sakura Ageha   桜あげは
description:
Agnes, who was ridiculed in the social circles for being an unfashionable noble, happened to help Naserbert, the duke’s son, who had been betrothed to the Princess.

However, the Princess saw this and ordered Naserbert to marry Agnes as punishment.

Isn’t it terrible to marry me as a punishment? Look, he seems to hate it too. Wait, he doesn’t?

This is a story about an unfashionable noble and a duke’s son, who grow closer to each other.>
